snippet.title: Atlantis - Walkabout Mini Golf - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Long ago, the ancient city of Atlantis fell out of favor with the deities and submerged into the ocean deep... this Thursday, you get to discover our 16th course Walkabout Mini Golf built by the gods or the Atlanteans? Charge your headsets and make your plans for January 26th!
